Sentencas: In this work, La2-xSmxCe2O7 (x = 0, 0.05, 0.10, 0.15, 0.20) powders are synthesized by the glycine-nitrate combustion method.
Titulo: Probing the Transport Properties, Electrophoretic Deposition, and Electrochemical Performance of La2-x Sm x Ce2O7 Ceramics for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The effects of the Sm dopant on the phase structure, microstructure, and electrical properties of La2-xSmxCe2O7 ceramics were investigated.
Titulo: Probing the Transport Properties, Electrophoretic Deposition, and Electrochemical Performance of La2-x Sm x Ce2O7 Ceramics for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: All ceramics of La2-xSmxCe2O7 possess a disordered cubic fluorite structure.
Titulo: Probing the Transport Properties, Electrophoretic Deposition, and Electrochemical Performance of La2-x Sm x Ce2O7 Ceramics for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: At x = 0, the materials exhibit a biphasic nature consisting of F- and C-type phases.
Titulo: Probing the Transport Properties, Electrophoretic Deposition, and Electrochemical Performance of La2-x Sm x Ce2O7 Ceramics for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: With increasing x value, the amount of the C-type phase decreases.

Sentencas: The La1.95Sm0.05Ce2O7 exhibits the highest ionic conductivity of 3.7 x 10(-3) S cm(-1) at 700 degrees C in a moist environment.
